snippet.title: ONE PIECE Pirate Warriors 4 - Tokyo Game Show Trailer | PS4, X1, NSW, PC
snippet.description:
ONE PIECE Pirate Warriors 4 includes an all-new original story in a mysterious land. . . Welcome to Wano Country. . .

Take on thousands of foes as Carrot, the fierce rabbit Mink of the Warrior Beast Tribe when she joins the playable roster in ONE PIECE Pirate Warriors 4! 

ONE PIECE Pirate Warriors 4 is coming in 2020.
